headline: Ross Stores, Inc. Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: DUBLIN, Calif., May 08, 2025--Ross Stores, Inc. (Nasdaq: ROST) plans to release its first quarter 2025 earnings results on Thursday, May 22, 2025 at approximately 4:00 p.m. Eastern time.
